Package: crispRvariants
Title: Tools for counting and visualising mutations in a target location
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Helen", family = "Lindsay", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "helen.lindsay@uzh.ch"))
Description: crispRvariants provides tools for counting and displaying variant
    combinations within a target region.
Depends:
